INSPIRATION
The general loop concept (trigger/action/verify/stop, self-paced vs.
fixed-interval) was inspired by Matthew Berman's (Forward Future) Loop
Library: https://signals.forwardfuture.ai/loop-library/
No text or tables from that source or from the community mirror
az9713/loop-library were copied — only the general, non-copyrightable
concept was independently described and developed into the
domain recipes in this repo.

